Package: jt-pve-storage-purestorage
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         proxmox-ve (>= 9.1) | pve-manager (>= 9.1),
         libwww-perl,
         libjson-perl,
         liburi-perl,
         open-iscsi,
         multipath-tools,
         sg3-utils,
         psmisc
Recommends: lsscsi
Description: Pure Storage FlashArray Storage Plugin for Proxmox VE
 This plugin enables Proxmox VE to use Pure Storage FlashArray for VM
 disk storage via iSCSI or Fibre Channel protocol.
 .
 Features:
  - Direct volume provisioning
  - Snapshot create/delete/rollback
  - Instant clone via Pure Storage snapshots
  - Multipath I/O support
  - Cluster-aware for live migration
  - Support for both iSCSI and Fibre Channel
